race.comment: MIA ZIPPER (1) was a flying 22.33 winner at Maitland last start. Can measure up again if runs up to latest time. RUINATION (7) continued his winning form with another strong run after leading making it three on end, scoring at this track over 324m (17.60). Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and a minor placing from five starts. In sparkling form with a string of wins and can measure up again. ELITE CHEVY (6) brought up her 10th career win last start at this track (17.56). Form here at the trip excellent including seven wins. Can make it back-to-back wins. DESPICABLE DASH (4) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - should be thereabouts.
